dc_title_s: Carta del corridoio Bizantino : la toponomastica e i confini
dc_description_s: Topograpic map overlayed with information showing the Byzantine Corridor; survey of toponyms origins; probable battle fields; and historical sites. Relief shown by spot heights. Grid: Gauss-Boaga - Fuso Est. At head of title: "Regione dell'Umbria, area Assetto del territorio - PUT." "Tavola I." Based on topographic map titled: "Carta della Regione Umbria." Original map is filed with companion volume in Firestone Library, call number: DG975.U5 C677 1999
dc_publisher_s: Spoleto : Centro italiano di studi sull'alto Medioevo, 1999.
